# Misc
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Patch files
*.patch
*.diff

# Core dumps
core

# Coverage reports
coverage/
*.coverage
htmlcov/

# Node (if any tooling is added)
node_modules/
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
